      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NUGGET ROBERTS (1) was safely held in tougher company last start after being shuffled back early at this track, but prior to that won by 0.8 lengths at this track (17.06) beating Shamrock Lady in a Grade 4/5 on May 26. Has claims if he runs up to expectations. WILGUNYA KNIGHT (7) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by 1.75 lengths at this track in a handy 16.88. Outside box to overcome but likes the trip. Must be included in calculations. OSCAR DUTTON (2) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 5.5 lengths at this track in a handy 16.72 beating Darby Display. Has never missed the frame from six starts from this draw, including three wins. Capable of going well again. SNAKE AND LADDER (8) is another with top-three prospects.",
